# Managed by Castellan - SSH listening port (2.6). Do not edit by hand.
# On Ubuntu 24.04 the sshd-socket-generator reads this Port and configures
# ssh.socket on daemon-reload; on a direct sshd.service it is used as-is. The
# address family (and thus IPv4/IPv6 bind) follows AddressFamily in the hardening
# drop-in, so the generator binds the right protocol.
Port {{ ssh_port }}
